  if n = 0 then " (WB ".&lt;1>.") "
  else if n mod 2 = 0 then square (spower (n/2) x)
  else x * (spower (n-1) x)")
      (CodeB "⇝    Characters 114-130:
  else if n mod 2 = 0 then square (spower (n/2) x)
                                  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Error: This expression has type int code
but an expression was expected of type int")
      "类型检查器再次报错, 不过这次是在另一个位置: "
      (Code "spower") "会生成之后将给出一个" (Code "int")
